CEnumerator

Generic enumerator object that can be used for dynamically generated array members.  It requires that the object defines a MaxIndex() function.  To make an object iterable, make sure to define the MaxIndex() function and insert this function in the class definition:

_NewEnum()
{
   return new CEnumerator(this)
}
